WorkBuddy China Legal Skills

This repository is a China-context adaptation of the upstream "Claude for Legal"
materials originally published by Anthropic PBC.

Upstream attribution:

  Project: Claude for Legal
  Repository: https://github.com/anthropics/claude-for-legal
  Copyright: Copyright 2026 Anthropic PBC
  License: Apache License, Version 2.0

This adaptation preserves the upstream legal-workflow structure and modifies it
for WorkBuddy and Mainland China legal/compliance contexts. Major adaptation
areas include:

  - WorkBuddy-oriented plugin metadata and configuration paths.
  - Mainland China as the default jurisdiction unless another jurisdiction is
    explicitly specified.
  - Added global and module-level China legal context references.
  - Added Chinese triggers and WorkBuddy China-context override sections to
    SKILL.md files.
  - Adjusted terminology for PRC legal, regulatory, corporate, labor,
    privacy/data, AI, IP, product, and dispute-resolution workflows.
  - Added warnings that outputs are drafts for legal/professional review and
    not legal advice.

The adaptation does not represent Anthropic's, WorkBuddy's, Tencent's, or any
other third party's legal positions.
